{"tid":368401,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"蒜蓉粉絲貴妃蚌","createTime":"2017-08-21T13:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T05:31:15.000Z","uid":123204,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3d1c491d4970062df31fa0c4f1e372f82de5ceb","tid":368401,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:48:26.000Z","msg":"話說今日行街市見到幾檔都賣貴妃蚌 大大隻<br />\n20蚊斤<br />\n又未食過<br />\n就的起心肝買咗兩斤<br />\n諗住蒜蓉粉絲蒸實無死<br />\n點知阿姐一磅收50蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2斤半原來得8隻 到底係我比人昆咗買海水定太好肉<br />\n阿姐為咗教我開殼同show 我睇啲蚌幾有肉<br />\n比完錢即席開我啲蚌睇 ❨用刀插入去轉一個圈❩<br />\n仲補一句 你食先好開啊 唔係一開就死咗<br />\n但你又開咗我嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返到去費咗九牛二虎之力 開殼 洗內臟 起肉<br />\n要訣係按一按個肉心 唧曬啲深色嘢出黎<br />\n搞咗一輪 成隻根本散曬執返埋一舊<br />\n如圖<img src=\"https://holland.pk/85pn30js\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F85pn30js&h=eaae4873&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9741cb963e48dc08f12e35dff3b7dcef4a4934c1","tid":368401,"uid":24139,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:56:37.000Z","msg":"蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b9f9e100357919cad6b9bc5a641a0baafe82fa","tid":368401,"uid":135284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e9d15d52c1fa658756c654ddaf12b1179be622","tid":368401,"uid":138799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:15:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5f82cd68eeeb053a7323d27e9fa95a3a1d5033","tid":368401,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行開咗 而家打"},{"pid":"613b267532b87a083e03c1ec0ffaed11ad4dc7ad","tid":368401,"uid":62856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[quote]蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行開咗 而家打[/quote蒜蓉粉絲呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0950b33dd6c1808d336f45bccb0a1788b0099ae5","tid":368401,"uid":123204,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o8lhp20r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo8lhp20r&h=307acd66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半個鐘前浸定粉絲<br />\n上蚌面<br />\n再壓啲蒜蓉 ❨用拉面鋪壓蒜支野❩ 上粉絲面<br />\n落少少玫瑰鹽<br />\n入爐蒸12分鐘<br />\n阿姐話蒸6分鐘<br />\n因為同埋有條班仔蒸埋一份所以耐啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/91pe0lgm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F91pe0lgm&h=7d531d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n燒紅啲米糠油 讚上去<br />\n再落一湯匙豉油即成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蚌肉又真係幾鮮同埋幾彈牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n洗蚌功夫未到家有少少沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然識食梗係食粉絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加埋啲油同豉油<br />\n再撈一撈蚌殼入面啲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96067160fbc92cf90790c33a51d55ddc8287e0c8","tid":368401,"uid":123204,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/frxm0igw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffrxm0igw&h=e4cc1737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再影一張<br />\n粉絲浸完煎開一半長度就容易啲放上去<br />\n<br />\n總結<br />\n50蚊黎講都真係唔錯<br />\n材料都唔煩<br />\n加啲粉絲 鹽 熱油同豉油已夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一般家庭都唔洗專登再買料<br />\n但係開殼同洗內臟真係搞咗好耐 ❨20分鐘到❩ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次都係整其他算"},{"pid":"936bd88cb0bf8a24c5335563790b8e8c8c10d0fd","tid":368401,"uid":3508,"like":4,"dislike":55,"score":-51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:34:32.000Z","msg":"我都係第一次見人蒸海鮮，粉絲係放係d海鮮面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2c75f75641fa2d21c62338039f27962dbdcc7d","tid":368401,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:35:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係第一次見人蒸海鮮，粉絲係放係d海鮮面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nexactly 擺錯咗 所以先要再撈黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吸經下次做返啱"},{"pid":"53f4c5d4a8064d84e41f00e8f0e4ca184730d546","tid":368401,"uid":49730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係第一次見人蒸海鮮，粉絲係放係d海鮮面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nexactly 擺錯咗 所以先要再撈黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吸經下次做返啱</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68aaaf267a9ca147d41faad1e85859a6687aff4e","tid":368401,"uid":138799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"媽媽話買開60蚊5 6隻 <br />\n應該大隻過你個啲<br />\n<br />\nbtw阿姐試過話蒸2分鐘<br />\n阿媽真係蒸咁耐<br />\n食到唔想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac5aae11cbe29f6d374c57ad59d05cfdcc5ce0d","tid":368401,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:44:21.000Z","msg":"入面有條類似魚翅咁既野，記得吱出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45d5979f385ef99104855c8b6396797875befa7","tid":368401,"uid":73356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>媽媽話買開60蚊5 6隻 <br />\n應該大隻過你個啲<br />\n<br />\nbtw阿姐試過話蒸2分鐘<br />\n阿媽真係蒸咁耐<br />\n食到唔想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  食生既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cb3bd7f6d698e6c007ab1da79e6c26a368e665","tid":368401,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>媽媽話買開60蚊5 6隻 <br />\n應該大隻過你個啲<br />\n<br />\nbtw阿姐試過話蒸2分鐘<br />\n阿媽真係蒸咁耐<br />\n食到唔想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2分鐘得唔得架"},{"pid":"1ea4d1bee06a90152a6729a127648710ebf31042","tid":368401,"uid":123204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入面有條類似魚翅咁既野，記得吱出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有幾隻無吱到<br />\n不過我食咗3隻都咁好彩無食到<br />\n有伏?"},{"pid":"bdd4c642b9cdc35dc68a30dd77bbd64fe77a25cc","tid":368401,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>媽媽話買開60蚊5 6隻 <br />\n應該大隻過你個啲<br />\n<br />\nbtw阿姐試過話蒸2分鐘<br />\n阿媽真係